comments: Batum (LAC) brings his hand toward Simons' (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs with Simons' front as he dribbles up the floor.
Nurkic (POR) is already in Morris Sr.'s (LAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Diabate (LAC) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another in the lane.

Jackson (LAC) brings his right forearm forward as he moves toward Nurkic (POR) and marginal contact occurs with Nurkic's front as he makes the pass. Diabate (LAC) absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs with Nurkic simultaneously.
Batum (LAC) contests the floater attempt and marginal contact occurs with Hart's (POR) slightly extended left forearm after the release.
Winslow (POR) and Jackson (LAC) come together at the same spot during the inbound and marginal contact occurs before they separate.
Simons (POR) engages and disengages with Powell (LAC) as Powell moves toward the midcourt line.
Jackson (LAC) establishes the ball in the frontcourt within eight seconds.
Simons (POR) is turning alongside Powell's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs prior to Powell's gather.

Simons (POR) brings his right arm forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Powell's (LAC) left forearm after his gather. Simons and Powell then make incidental foot-to-foot contact as they return to the floor following the release of the driving shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) and Simons (POR) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.

Jackson (LAC) brushes Simons' (POR) left forearm and marginal contact occurs after Simons' gather. Batum (LAC) is turning away from Simons and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs thereafter. Diabate (LAC) then cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Winslow (POR) brings his right arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Jackson's (LAC) front after Jackson retrieves the rebound.
Jackson (LAC) fumbles the ball after initially making contact with it during rebounding, comes to a stop, and legally starts his dribble after establishing full control of the ball.
Winslow (POR) turns slightly toward Jackson (LAC) and marginal contact occurs as Jackson dribbles near half-court.
Winslow (POR) slows his forward momentum prior to marginal body contact occurring with Jackson's (LAC) back as Jackson comes to a stop inside the perimeter.
Nurkic's (POR) foot avoids making contact with the ball as Jackson (LAC) loses control of it near the elbow.

Diabate (LAC) establishes himself in Simons' (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the defensive switch simultaneously occurs. Diabate and Simons then briefly engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Nurkic (POR) turns with his right forearm brought forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Powell's (LAC) front/side after his gather.
Simons (POR) engages and disengages with Diabate (LAC) as Diabate moves to establish rebounding position.
Diabate (LAC) and Winslow (POR) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each pursue the rebound.
Diaabte (LAC) initiates contact with Nurkic's (POR) front and lower body off-ball, causing Nurkic to become dislodged.
Batum (LAC) engages and disengages with Simons (POR) during the inbound.
Batum (LAC) cleanly blocks Simons' (POR) driving shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it toward the baseline as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs with Watford (POR) during rebounding.
Simons (POR) extends his left arm forward into Powell's (LAC) path and initiates contact with Powell's front/arm.
Diabate (LAC) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Nurkic (POR) slightly extends to the side as he establishes his screening position and marginal contact occurs with Powell (LAC) as Powell goes around the screen.
Powell (LAC) legally contests Simons' (POR) jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Simons' lower body after the release.
Diabate (LAC) engages with Nurkic (POR) in the lane and disengages as the ball falls to the opposite corner during the long rebound.
Jackson's (LAC) left foot stays in bounds as he retrieves the rebound.
Watford (POR) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) retreats his left hand away from Simons' (POR) side and does not apply any force as Simons starts his upward shooting motion.
